Mobile operator MTN has launched new “Social” data bundles on its network, MyBroadband reports. The data bundles are available for WhatsApp, Facebook, YouTube, and Twitter, and can be purchased in different sizes and validity periods, it said. The deals can be accessed via MTN’s USSD menu, by dialling *136*2# and selecting option 5. “MTN confirmed to MyBroadband it will officially launch great-value social media bundles this week, and has good news to share with its customers, but did not provide further details,” it said. According to MTN’s USSD menu,  bundles include 1GB / 30 days for R10.00 using WhatsApp or Twitter, and or 1GB / 30 days for R50.00 on Facebook and Youtube. The full pricing structure can be found on MyBroadband, here. Read: MTN has the best mobile network in South Africa: research